badgeType.description: The badge-type logo type is divided into dots "dot" and text "text", and the badge-type is not displayed if the badge-type is not set
badgeType.description_zh: 徽标类型 badge-type 分为圆点“dot”和文本“text”，不设置 badge-type 则不显示徽标

badgeText.description: If badge-type is text, the number in the logo will not take effect if badge-type="text" is empty
badgeText.description_zh: badge-type 为 text 的时候，徽标内的数字，为空时badge-type="text"不生效
